---
const TIMEPAD_URL = 'https://fczt.timepad.ru/events/';
---
<section class="events" id="events">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="events__grid">
      <div class="events__head reveal">
        <div class="sec-tag">События клуба</div>
        <h2 class="events__title">
          ВСТРЕЧИ,<br/>
          <span>МАТЧИ,</span><br/>
          СОБРАНИЯ
        </h2>
        <p class="events__lead">
          Записывайтесь на встречи с командой, открытые тренировки,
          собрания болельщиков и товарищеские матчи.
          Регистрация и билеты — через&nbsp;Timepad.
        </p>
        <a class="events__cta" href={TIMEPAD_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Все мероприятия
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="events__visual reveal-right">
        <div class="events__card">
          <div class="events__card-tag">TIMEPAD</div>
          <div class="events__card-row">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="events__card-title">Открытые тренировки</div>
              <div class="events__card-meta">Бесплатно · по расписанию</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="events__card-row">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="events__card-title">Встречи с командой</div>
              <div class="events__card-meta">После домашних матчей</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="events__card-row">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="events__card-title">Собрания болельщиков</div>
              <div class="events__card-meta">Ежемесячно</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="events__card-row">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="events__card-title">Товарищеские матчи</div>
              <div class="events__card-meta">Сезонно</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="events__card-foot">
            Полное расписание и регистрация — на странице клуба&nbsp;на&nbsp;Timepad.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .events {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: #ffffff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .events::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -200px; right: -200px;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(228,0,43,0.05), transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(50px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .events__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .events__head { max-width: 540px; }
  .events__title {
    font-family: 'Onest', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }
  .events__title span { color: #E4002B; }
  .events__lead {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 36px;
  }

  .events__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px 28px;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Onest', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    border: 1px solid #0a0a0a;
  }
  .events__cta:hover {
    background: #E4002B;
    border-color: #E4002B;
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .events__cta .arrow {
    font-size: 18px;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .events__cta:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

  /* Card */
  .events__visual { position: relative; }
  .events__card {
    background: #fafaf7;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    position: relative;
  }
  .events__card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 6px;
    background: #E4002B;
  }
  .events__card-tag {
    font-family: 'Onest', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: #E4002B;
    margin-bottom: 26px;
  }
  .events__card-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .events__card-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: 0; }
  .dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    background: #E4002B;
    margin-top: 7px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  .events__card-title {
    font-family: 'Onest', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .events__card-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6a6a6a;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .events__card-foot {
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .events { padding: 80px 0; }
    .events__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }
</style>
